00:09:37,187 --> 00:09:38,902
vi oyf, oyf di knies.

214
00:09:40,444 --> 00:09:42,361
un dernokh dem, in mitn der nakht...

215
00:09:42,857 --> 00:09:45,095
s'iz geven zeyer a regn mit a vint...

216
00:09:46,350 --> 00:09:47,626
iz in shlof,

217
00:09:47,869 --> 00:09:49,128
UNK shloft,

218
00:09:49,135 --> 00:09:51,339
vi me git mir emetser a klap.

219
00:09:51,649 --> 00:09:53,432
ikh hob mir gegibn a khap oyf,

220
00:09:55,007 --> 00:09:58,150
un s'-, un s'iz vi zi zogt mir, "antloyf!

221
00:09:58,150 --> 00:10:00,232
antloyf, vayl m'vet dir haynt shisn!"

222
00:10:00,762 --> 00:10:05,112
hob ikh gezogt der khevre, "kumt, lomir loyfn!" un zey hobn nisht, shoyn nisht gekent zikh oyfheybn.

223
00:10:05,112 --> 00:10:07,151
zey hobn gezogt az zey kenen shoyn nisht geyn.

224
00:10:07,157 --> 00:10:09,783
un ikh hob pamelekh aroysgekrokhn.

225
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,656
kh'hob gevust dort umedum.

226
00:10:12,422 --> 00:10:14,925
un di, abi ikh bin aroysge⟨gan⟩ oyfn shosey,

227
00:10:14,925 --> 00:10:17,057
hot mir nokhgeshosn di politsey.

228
00:10:17,367 --> 00:10:19,224
ikh bin arayn in a ander shtub.

229
00:10:19,695 --> 00:10:22,265
un arayn dort, un a farbaheltenish iz geven.

230
00:10:22,265 --> 00:10:24,076
⟨un ikh bin⟩ aroyf oyf a pekelik,

231
00:10:24,133 --> 00:10:27,910
un UNK un in der zayt iz geshtanen tsugeshtelt a shank

232
00:10:27,947 --> 00:10:30,754
mit a tirele UNK ⟨zikh⟩ dort geefnt un ikh bin arayn.

233
00:10:30,754 --> 00:10:34,224
bin ikh gelign a gantsn tog dort farbahaltn, un zey zenen nokh,

234
00:10:34,224 --> 00:10:35,724
un zey hobn gezukht in shtub,

235
00:10:35,724 --> 00:10:37,976
un zey hobn keynem nisht gefunen, zenen zey avekgegan.

236
00:10:37,976 --> 00:10:40,411
ale zakhn in shtub iz geven aroysgevorfn

237
00:10:40,502 --> 00:10:41,896
fun di shafes,

238
00:10:42,122 --> 00:10:44,512
un dortn bin ikh gelign a gantsn tog

239
00:10:45,666 --> 00:10:48,343
un, kler ikh, kh'hob moyre gehat aroptsugeyn.

240
00:10:49,024 --> 00:10:50,145
bay nakht...

241
00:10:50,145 --> 00:10:53,426
kh'hob gevust az zey veln di t- morgn oder iber morgn a tog,

242
00:10:53,426 --> 00:10:54,974
veln zey tsunemen di shafe,

243
00:10:55,116 --> 00:10:56,527
veln zey mir gefinen.

244
00:10:56,533 --> 00:10:58,180
bin ikh aropgekrokhn

245
00:10:58,660 --> 00:11:01,831
un aroysgekrokhn nokhn fentster. s'iz geven zeyer bay,

246
00:11:01,831 --> 00:11:02,788
shpet bay nakht

247
00:11:02,895 --> 00:11:05,943
un, fintster, regn, mit a vint.

248
00:11:06,085 --> 00:11:08,374
un ikh hob aribergekrokhn dem gortn

249
00:11:08,835 --> 00:11:11,664
in a, in a, in dem veg dortn,

250
00:11:11,772 --> 00:11:13,202
un ⟨ikh bin⟩ avek,

251
00:11:13,202 --> 00:11:14,955
genumen loyfn avek fun shtot.

252
00:11:15,197 --> 00:11:17,725
⟨un di⟩, oyf der gas, hob ikh gezen, m'iz gegan polits.

253
00:11:17,725 --> 00:11:19,528
ikh bin gelofn mit di felder.

254
00:11:19,703 --> 00:11:23,443
kh'hob gevolt loyfn tsu mir in shtetl arayn, finef un tsvontsik kilometer.

255
00:11:23,955 --> 00:11:26,277
ikh hob aroysgerisn a heyptl kroyt

256
00:11:26,301 --> 00:11:30,041
un gehaltn unter der hant. ikh hob geesn, vayl kh'hob shoyn a por tog gornisht nisht geesn.

257
00:11:30,081 --> 00:11:31,779
un azoy bin ikh gelofn

258
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:32,893
biz

259
00:11:33,692 --> 00:11:36,554
in der f- iz shoyn geven, ongehoybn vern likhtik.

260
00:11:37,776 --> 00:11:39,730
bin ikh arayn tsun eyner...

261
00:11:39,730 --> 00:11:41,533
ikh hob moyre gehat arayntsugeyn in shtetl arayn...

262
00:11:41,725 --> 00:11:43,873
bin ikh arayn tsun eyner a kristin,

263
00:11:43,873 --> 00:11:45,786
a bakante. hot zi mir gezogt

264
00:11:46,129 --> 00:11:50,409
az UNK gantse shtetl iz shoyn oysgeharget un s'iz keyner nishto.

265
00:11:50,972 --> 00:11:55,455
un ikh hob ir gebetn, zi zol mir gibn UNK a shtikl broyt. hot zi moyre gehat un zi hot mir gornisht gegibn.

266
00:11:55,697 --> 00:11:57,193
bin ikh avekgegangen,

267
00:11:57,368 --> 00:12:01,226
un gegangen dort vu me geyt pasen di beheymes, un gezitsn un geveynt,

268
00:12:01,738 --> 00:12:03,971
un geklert, "tsu vos hob ikh gedorfn blaybn?

269
00:12:03,971 --> 00:12:05,932
az s'iz, me zet nisht keynem, keyn mentsh.

270
00:12:05,932 --> 00:12:07,116
un vu zol ikh geyn?"

271
00:12:07,189 --> 00:12:09,832
un a gantsn tog bin ikh gelign farbahaltn in vald,

272
00:12:09,923 --> 00:12:12,029
un gerisn yagedes,

273
00:12:12,029 --> 00:12:14,641
 vos s'iz geven, un, un geesn.

274
00:12:15,137 --> 00:12:17,544
ikh hob moyre gehat, di pastekher zoln mir zen.

275
00:12:17,770 --> 00:12:19,584
un dernokh dem, far nakht,

276
00:12:19,879 --> 00:12:21,189
bin ikh avekgegan

277
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:22,460
mitn vald

278
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:23,614
in a dorf arayn,

279
00:12:23,614 --> 00:12:26,032
s'hot geheysn Bi- Budnikes.

280
00:12:26,089 --> 00:12:28,277
ikh hob dort gearbet bay a krist.

281
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:30,808
hob ikh geklert, "ikh'l arayngeyn tsu dem krist,

282
00:12:30,932 --> 00:12:32,831
vet er mir iberhaltn, efsher."

283
00:12:33,278 --> 00:12:37,292
m'hot zikh nisht gegleybt az azoy vet forkumen, m'vet yedn oyshargenen.

284
00:12:37,969 --> 00:12:38,978
zogt mir,

285
00:12:38,978 --> 00:12:43,190
kenen mir zikh kern a bisl tsurik? beys ir zayt geven in bahaltenish in LYUBOMIR,

286
00:12:43,404 --> 00:12:46,921
ver iz nokh ge- vifl mentshn zaynen gevezn mit aykh demolt?

287
00:12:47,503 --> 00:12:49,483
s'iz geven dem balebos's tokhter,

288
00:12:49,483 --> 00:12:51,598
un di vos m'hot tsugenumen, di,

289
00:12:53,005 --> 00:12:55,170
mit der froy, mitn kind, ir zun,

290
00:12:55,170 --> 00:12:57,797
a groyser zun shoyn, a draytsn, fertsn yor efsher.

291
00:12:57,966 --> 00:12:59,760
un s'iz nokh geven a por yidn alte,

292
00:12:59,620 --> 00:13:01,774
ir gedenkt nit vi m'hot zey gerufn?

293
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:02,617
vos ikh hob zey nisht gekent. NO, kh'hob zey nisht gekent, di yidn.

294
00:13:02,404 --> 00:13:05,773
un ver iz mit aykh tsuzamen avekgelofn? ir zayt aleyn gelofn?

295
00:13:05,408 --> 00:13:08,625
keyner nisht; zey hobn nisht gekent geyn. zey hobn gezogt, zey kenen nisht geyn.

296
00:13:08,698 --> 00:13:10,539
m'hot shoyn nisht gekent oyfheybn zikh.

297
00:13:11,112 --> 00:13:12,878
on esn, on gornisht.

298
00:13:15,330 --> 00:13:18,530
iz, vos iz mit zey pa- dernokh geshen? veyst ir nit?

299
00:13:18,925 --> 00:13:21,853
zenen zikh nisht geven, ⟨ge⟩kumen, me, m'hot shoyn nisht gelebt.

300
00:13:21,853 --> 00:13:23,651
m'hot zey aroysgenumen, m'hot zey derharget.

301
00:13:24,409 --> 00:13:25,685
keyner iz nisht geblibn.

302
00:13:26,333 --> 00:13:30,393
ya, zayt ir gekumen tsu dem poyer bay velkhn ir hot gearbet, UNK...

303
00:13:29,016 --> 00:13:30,967
ikh bin arayngekumen tsu dem poyer,

304
00:13:30,999 --> 00:13:33,684
⟨iz⟩ geven bay nakht. zogt er, "zets zikh arop oyf der erd."

305
00:13:33,994 --> 00:13:37,143
vayl er hot moyre gehat, nokh di fentster, me zol mir nisht zen emetser.

306
00:13:38,213 --> 00:13:39,954
un er hot mir gegibn a shtikl broyt

307
00:13:39,954 --> 00:13:41,261
mit a bisl milekh.

308
00:13:41,892 --> 00:13:43,887
zogt er, "her oys, Leyzer."

309
00:13:43,887 --> 00:13:46,391
er hot mir gekent vayl ikh hob bay im gearbet a por vokhn.

310
00:13:47,713 --> 00:13:49,696
zogt er, "ikh ken dir nisht farbahaltn,

311
00:13:49,696 --> 00:13:52,669
vayl in shtal hob ikh tsvey yidishe meydlekh farbahaltene.

312
00:13:54,143 --> 00:13:56,561
bald," zogt er, "kumt funem vald eyn yingl,

313
00:13:56,561 --> 00:13:59,182
vayl er kumt oft un ikh gib im a broyt.

314
00:14:00,032 --> 00:14:04,413
vestu mit zey avekgeyn in vald arayn, un dortn vestu zayn mit zey vu zey veln zayn."

315
00:14:05,365 --> 00:14:08,981
keyn breyre hob ikh nisht gehat, un s'hot nisht gedoyert lang, iz gekumen dos yingl.

316
00:14:08,981 --> 00:14:11,033
dos yingl iz geven fun dem dorf.

317
00:14:11,845 --> 00:14:12,986
a yidisher?

318
00:14:12,604 --> 00:14:13,880
a yidisher bokher.

319
00:14:13,937 --> 00:14:16,112
un er hot mir mitgenumen in vald arayn.

320
00:14:16,266 --> 00:14:18,352
⟨kh'bin⟩ gekumen in vald, s'iz geven bay nakht,

321
00:14:18,443 --> 00:14:20,782
iz geven fun mayn shtetl dray yidn,

322
00:14:21,345 --> 00:14:23,212
shkheynim, vos ikh hob zey gekent,

323
00:14:23,488 --> 00:14:25,152
un s'iz gevezn nokh

324
00:14:25,294 --> 00:14:28,393
a yid, oykhet fun dem dorf, fun Budnikes.

325
00:14:28,652 --> 00:14:30,738
azoy ze'mir dort gezitsn

326
00:14:30,998 --> 00:14:33,557
biz s'iz nokh geven di bleter oyf di beymer.

327
00:14:33,681 --> 00:14:34,957
dos iz gevezn

328
00:14:35,672 --> 00:14:38,214
oktober, efsher onheyb november.

329
00:14:39,267 --> 00:14:40,445
un,

330
00:14:40,445 --> 00:14:42,349
mir fleg'mir bay nakht geyn

331
00:14:43,215 --> 00:14:46,449
ganvenen kartoflyes. m'hot gevust vu s'iz do di griber,

332
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:49,388
fleg men aroysshlepn kartoflyes,

333
00:14:49,388 --> 00:14:52,406
un dos hot men gekokht a bisl vaser mit di kartoflyes.

334
00:14:52,716 --> 00:14:54,366
dernokh dem, az s'iz gevorn

335
00:14:54,366 --> 00:14:55,798
aroys der shney,

336
00:14:56,597 --> 00:14:58,295
un s'iz gevorn farfroyrn,

337
00:14:58,909 --> 00:15:01,485
un m'hot shoyn nisht gekent geyn nemen di kartoflyes,

338
00:15:04,090 --> 00:15:06,660
un me, un di pastekher hobn shoyn ongehoybn geyn

339
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:08,843
traybn pasen di beheymes in vald.

340
00:15:09,152 --> 00:15:10,901
hobn zey undz bamerkt.

341
00:15:12,628 --> 00:15:14,760
mir ze'mir gelign in aza budke,

342
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:16,470
ale geshlofn in,

343
00:15:16,915 --> 00:15:20,031
genumen un fardekt mit lozes, me zol undz nisht derkenen.

344
00:15:21,133 --> 00:15:26,145
un, mit a mol her'mir, az di daytshn zenen geven un zey hobn tsugekhapt,

345
00:15:26,145 --> 00:15:29,703
tsugenumen beyde meydlekh, vayl di meydlekh zenen gelign bazunder fun undz.

346
00:15:29,703 --> 00:15:32,383
hot men zey avekgefirt in shtetl arayn, keyn Opalin,

347
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:35,116
un zey hobn gezogt, zey hobn gold ⟨tsu⟩ gibn zey.

348
00:15:35,882 --> 00:15:38,857
 ober zey hobn gornisht gehat, hot men zey geshosn in shtetl.

349
00:15:38,857 --> 00:15:40,950
tsvey meydlekh: eyne iz geven fun Opalin

350
00:15:40,950 --> 00:15:42,845
un eyne iz geven fun Budnikes.

351
00:15:43,341 --> 00:15:45,529
⟨inem⟩, in a tsvey tog arum,

352
00:15:45,636 --> 00:15:47,300
in der fri, mir shtey'mir

353
00:15:47,374 --> 00:15:50,966
barn fayer, arum un arum. mir va- viln zikh onvaremen fun bay nakht.

354
00:15:51,947 --> 00:15:54,675
her'mir vi se git a brekh zikh epes a shtekele,

355
00:15:54,698 --> 00:15:56,255
fun di, di trukene,

356
00:15:56,255 --> 00:15:57,644
di tsvayglekh.

357
00:15:57,803 --> 00:16:01,529
un eyner,... iz geven a yid a hoykher. H- Hersh hot er geheysn...

358
00:16:01,529 --> 00:16:03,078
hot zikh ibergedreyt dem kop,

359
00:16:03,152 --> 00:16:05,356
hot er gezogt, "zey zenen shoyn do."

360
00:16:05,650 --> 00:16:07,334
un azoy vi er hot dos gezogt,

361
00:16:07,334 --> 00:16:09,457
hobn zey ongehoybn shtark shisn,

362
00:16:10,341 --> 00:16:12,663
un ikh mit nokh eynem bokher,

363
00:16:12,703 --> 00:16:16,022
fun Budnikes, ze'mir genumen, ⟨ho'mir⟩ genumen antloyfn

364
00:16:16,022 --> 00:16:18,384
tsishn di kortshes un ze'mir avek un avek.

365
00:16:18,778 --> 00:16:21,387
dernokh dem, efsher in a sho arum, ho'mir gehert

366
00:16:21,951 --> 00:16:23,160
oyfn veg

367
00:16:23,318 --> 00:16:26,056
vi m'hot oysgeshosn fir mol.

368
00:16:27,283 --> 00:16:30,719
hob ikh gezogt tsum, tsum bokher az mistam hot men shoyn derharget di yidn.

369
00:16:31,182 --> 00:16:34,292
s'iz gevorn fintster. hot der bokher gezogt, "kum, ⟨vel'mir⟩ tsugeyn

370
00:16:34,292 --> 00:16:35,279
oyfn veg,

371
00:16:35,279 --> 00:16:36,440
vel'mir zen

372
00:16:36,953 --> 00:16:38,719
tsi s'iz do emetser fun di yidn."

373
00:16:38,978 --> 00:16:40,198
⟨un ze'mir⟩ tsugegan,

374
00:16:40,198 --> 00:16:42,515
zenen zey gelign dort oyfn veg barn brikl,

375
00:16:42,538 --> 00:16:43,780
ale dray.

376
00:16:44,226 --> 00:16:45,651
geven geshosn.

377
00:16:46,605 --> 00:16:48,134
ze'mir zey gelozt.

378
00:16:48,664 --> 00:16:52,235
⟨un, un i-⟩ mir ze'mir avekgegangen tsurik in vald arayn. zogt der bokher,

379
00:16:52,393 --> 00:16:54,187
"ikh bin fun dem dorf.

380
00:16:54,187 --> 00:16:56,980
ikh vel geyn ⟨in⟩, hob ikh bakante, kh'vel geyn,

381
00:16:56,980 --> 00:16:58,597
vet mir efsher farbahaltn.

382
00:16:58,772 --> 00:17:01,466
un du hob ikh nisht vu," zogt er, "tsu nemen."

383
00:17:00,983 --> 00:17:02,732
vi hot men gerufn dem bokher?

384
00:17:02,738 --> 00:17:03,980
ikh gedenk nisht.

385
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:06,134
er iz geven a Budniker bokher.

386
00:17:06,821 --> 00:17:08,620
un ikh bin geblibn aleyn.

387
00:17:08,661 --> 00:17:12,393
ikh hob im ⟨nokh⟩ gegibn mayns a hemd. ikh hob gehat tsvey eybershte hemdlekh

388
00:17:12,393 --> 00:17:15,381
ongetun. zog ikh, "na dir a hemd, vayl du host nisht gornisht vos ontsutun."

389
00:17:16,626 --> 00:17:19,455
un ikh bin geblibn, klern vos tut men,

390
00:17:20,742 --> 00:17:25,933
vu tsu geyn. un di vegn hob ikh dort gevust, vayl ikh fleg in di derfer ale arbetn.

391
00:17:26,168 --> 00:17:27,460
s'iz geven bay nakht,

392
00:17:27,460 --> 00:17:29,134
bin ikh tsugegan tsun eyn shtub,

393
00:17:29,417 --> 00:17:33,752
a bakanter. hob ikh ongeklapt az me zol mir gibn a shtikl broyt. hot er mir gegibn a shtikl broyt

394
00:17:33,752 --> 00:17:35,351
un er hot mir gezogt, "shoyn antloyf."

395
00:17:36,387 --> 00:17:38,895
dernokh dem bin ikh arayngegan nokh tsun eyner a kristin.

396
00:17:39,762 --> 00:17:43,213
hot zi mir davke arayngenumen in shtub arayn, gegibn a bisl SOUP.

397
00:17:44,098 --> 00:17:47,264
un azoy vi ikh bin gezitsn, iz arayngekumen a shokhn,

398
00:17:47,372 --> 00:17:48,516
a krist.

399
00:17:48,739 --> 00:17:52,524
der shokhn iz avekgegan. zogt zi, "yetst ken ikh dir shoyn nisht haltn do,

400
00:17:52,524 --> 00:17:54,878
vayl der ⟨g-⟩ der shokhn hot gezen, bist do,

401
00:17:54,878 --> 00:17:56,168
hob ikh moyre⟨n⟩."

402
00:17:56,168 --> 00:17:57,811
hot zi gezogt, "gey arayn in shtal.

403
00:17:57,852 --> 00:18:00,934
vestu z- iberzayn di nakht mit di beheymes dortn.

404
00:18:01,513 --> 00:18:02,671
in der fri,"

405
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:06,063
