406
00:18:06,154 --> 00:18:08,696
mit a por kartoflyes un geheysn avekgeyn.

407
00:18:09,158 --> 00:18:11,126
un oyf der gas iz shoyn geven shney.

408
00:18:12,297 --> 00:18:14,417
⟨kh'bin⟩ gegangen un geveynt: "vu geyt men?"

409
00:18:14,794 --> 00:18:16,526
kh'hob nisht gehat vu ahintsutun zikh.

410
00:18:16,836 --> 00:18:19,108
dernokh dem bin ikh gegangen nokh tsu eyn krist.

411
00:18:19,603 --> 00:18:22,924
⟨kh'hob mir⟩ arayngeganvet nokhn hintershtn tirl. fleg zayn bay zey

412
00:18:22,924 --> 00:18:25,149
in di shtaln, ti- a tirl.

413
00:18:25,257 --> 00:18:26,584
bin ikh arayngegan,

414
00:18:26,657 --> 00:18:28,996
un ikh hob farbahaltn zikh untern hey.

